<paragraph id="8B9F3697DF7A1108FF44CC44FA2518A7" blockId="3.[151,1436,1273,2034]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">
<emphasis id="B954EA85DF7A1108FF44CC44FE611802" bold="true" box="[198,472,1853,1879]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">Nomenclatural notes:</emphasis>
―Because of the previous existence of the name 
<taxonomicName id="4C204D14DF7A1108FBC4CC44FEA5182B" authority="Hackel (1909: 312" authorityName="Hackel" authorityYear="1909" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Paspalum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="juergensii">
<emphasis id="B954EA85DF7A1108FBC4CC44FA851803" box="[1094,1340,1853,1878]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">Paspalum juergensii</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB14B66DF7A1108FACBCC44FEA5182B" author="Hackel, E." pageId="3" pageNumber="63" pagination="311 - 327" refId="ref3994" refString="Hackel, E. (1909) Gramineae novae VI. Repertorium Specierum Novarum Regni Vegetabilis 7: 311 - 327." type="journal article" year="1909">Hackel (1909: 312</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, ‘jürgensii’), referring to a different species, the combination resulting from the transference of 
<taxonomicName id="4C204D14DF7A1108FF15CCF2FE5318F1" authority="Hackel" authorityName="Hackel" authorityYear="1915" box="[151,490,1930,1956]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Panicum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="juergensii">
<emphasis id="B954EA85DF7A1108FF15CCF2FE3018F1" box="[151,393,1931,1956]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">Panicum juergensii</emphasis>
Hackel
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName id="4C204D14DF7A1108FD97CCF2FD2918F1" box="[533,656,1931,1956]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Paspalum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B954EA85DF7A1108FD97CCF2FD2918F1" box="[533,656,1931,1956]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">Paspalum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
would be a later homonym. Thus, the species must be called 
<taxonomicName id="4C204D14DF7A1108FF15CCC8FE14189F" authorityName="Chase ex G. H. Rua &amp; Valls" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="Chase ex G. H. Rua &amp; Valls" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[151,429,1969,1994]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Paspalum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rawitscheri">
<emphasis id="B954EA85DF7A1108FF15CCC8FE14189F" box="[151,429,1969,1994]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">Paspalum rawitscheri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on the earliest available epithet (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB14B66DF7A1108FC28CCC8FB13189E" author="McNeill, J. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Burdet, H. M. &amp; Demoulin, V. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; Nicolson, D. H. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Silva, P. C. &amp; Skog, J. E. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J. &amp; Gantner Verlag KG" box="[938,1194,1969,1995]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" refId="ref4209" refString="McNeill, J., Barrie, F. R., Burdet, H. M., Demoulin, V., Hawksworth, D. L., Marhold, K., Nicolson, D. H., Prado, J., Silva, P. C., Skog, J. E., Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J. (eds.) (2006) International Code of Botanical Nomenclature (Vienna Code). Regnum Vegetabile 146. A. R. G. Gantner Verlag KG, Ruggell, 568 pp." type="book" year="2006">
McNeill 
<emphasis id="B954EA85DF7A1108FB9CCCC8FBE6189F" box="[1054,1119,1969,1994]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
, Art. 11.4). Such a combination has been formerly made by Chase (unpublished manuscript) but was never effectively published.
</paragraph>
